UNITED STATES ex rel. Rachael GOLDBAUM and Raisel Goldbaum, Relators-Appellants, v. COMMISSIONER OF IMMIGRATION, etc., Respondent-Appellee. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. October 20, 1924.). No. 47. Joseph G. M. Browne, of New York City (Barnett E. Kopelman, of New York City, on the brief), for relators-appellants. William Hayward, U. S. Atty., of New York City, for respondent-appellee.

Before ROGERS, HOUGH, and MANTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order (298 F. 118) affirmed.
